text: Gary Eck is an Australian comedian and actor. He has been an actor and writer for many movies including, The Night We Call Day, Boy Town and Happy Feet Two. Eck has also starred in many comedy shows and produced his first CD, Gary Eck Live! In 2004 he was nominated for an ARIA Award for his movie comedy album The Hollywood Motel. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Australian comedians Category:Australian actors Category:Australian filmmakers Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people
